Hadoop and MapReduce learing

Task
Count words in big data

R script generates file with 100mln lines in format <Key \t Value\n>, Key - one of 12 words, Value = 1.
File simulates Mapper output file.
File's size of ~1.2GB is being generating.

Python scripts countMap.py and countReduce.py simulates Reducer in Hadoop MapReduce. Count unique words. countMap.py splits lines to words, countReduce.py counts words.
Python script MapReduce-one-function.py combines splitting and counting functions.
